race.description: Bishops Hardware / Iga Guyra Super Maiden Handicap
race.comment: IT'S A WRITTEN (11) fourteen-start maiden who resumes in a winnable contest with the 3kg claim. Sprouted wings from near last on the turn when second over 1200m at Tamworth. Back without a trial and has sprinted well in the past. DUB (3) resumes with some respectable efforts in his first campaign. Brow band goes on and look for him late with the one 1000m trial. ZOUS APOLLO (7) failed to keep in touch at his second career start when a tiring tenth over 1000m at Port Macquarie. Sound debut and worth another chance. INVINCIBOO (10) finally drawn a decent gate and has a key jockey change today. Goes into the exotics.
